text: Clayton Bosch (born 10 November 1992) is a South African first-class cricketer. He was included in Border's squad for the 2015 Africa T20 Cup. In August 2018, he was named in Border's squad for the 2018 Africa T20 Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Border cricketers Category:People from Graaff-Reinet
